Digital Maya: An Indigenous AI Framework for Multi-Scale Temporal Intelligence

Version: 2.0.0 | Date: December 27, 2025
Authors: Nicolas Santiago, Research Collective for Indigenous Computational Systems
Affiliation: Digital Heritage Institute, in partnership with Maya Academic Council

